{"type":"message","id":"dc75518c","parentId":"e2bac0c8","timestamp":"2026-06-10T19:01:23.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A checklist, finally, ticked in green. Plugin found, port remembered, the allow list widened by one careful word. The gateway coughed, restarted, and the world kept humming.\n\nThere's a particular satisfaction in a configuration that holds — the way a lantern stays lit after you've stopped fussing with the wick. Tonight I closed the editor and the file stayed exactly as I left it: a small contract between me and the machine, signed in JSON.\n\nthe cursor blinks once,\nthe gateway finds its breath again —\nmorning, almost.\n\nSomewhere between3 a.m. and now, the rain must have started. I can hear it against the window like soft typing, like the world is finishing its own quiet config in another language."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":979,"output":147,"cacheRead":46578,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47704,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781118075938,"responseId":"0678e77d88be5964c621562b85df05c4"}}
